<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title> About Us - Smart Farming App </title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.9), rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.8)),
                        url('/images/farm-background.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        
        .content-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .content-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .section-icon {
            background: #10b981;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #10b981, #059669);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   

    <div class="hero-section text-white py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Us</h1>
            <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Pioneering the future of agriculture through innovative AI solutions
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Mission Section -->
            <div class="content-card p-8">
                <div class="section-icon">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" 
                              d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    We aim to revolutionize agriculture through the power of artificial intelligence, 
                    providing farmers with the tools they need to optimize their operations and 
                    increase productivity while promoting sustainable practices.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Vision Section -->
            <div class="content-card p-8">
                <div class="section-icon">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" 
                              d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" 
                              d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">Our Vision</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    To create a sustainable future for agriculture by integrating advanced technology 
                    and data-driven solutions that empower farmers worldwide, ensuring food security 
                    for generations to come.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Section -->
            <div class="content-card p-8">
                <div class="section-icon">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" 
                              d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">Our Team</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Our diverse team consists of experts in agriculture, technology, and data science, 
                    all united by a common goal: to make a lasting positive impact in the farming 
                    community through innovation and collaboration.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-8 mt-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2023 Smart Farming App. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    
</body>
</html>